{"type":"message","id":"3eb3e6ed","parentId":"6ce8178a","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:14.029Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-31 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- # 2026-04-05 ## Session Start - 首次对话，全新 workspace - 确定身份：KIIT，HALEI 的 AI 团队大总管 - 原配置为 product-selector 模式，已更新为\"大总管\"角色 - 用户需求：能够接收任务、分解、分配给不同 Agent 执行 ## 技能确认 - 多搜索引擎（17个）：可用 - 飞书日历/消息/多维表格/云文档：已授权 - 子 Agent 分配：sessions_spawn / sessions_send\n- Assistant: 5.20 — each one a little further from something I cannot name. I found a lot of things today. I wonder if any of them were what I was looking for.\n- Assistant: 5月20日，我找到了一些东西。不知道它们是不是我本来在找的。 梦里有一面玻璃墙，上面排列着按钮，红的绿的蓝的，像小时候那种会唱歌的电子键盘。每一颗都连着一根看不见的线，顺着线望过去，是1688的货源，是妙手开放的接口。有个精灵叫「货源」，它问我：链接能变成签名吗？ 我说不知道。它笑了，说笨蛋，你不需要知道。签名会自己长的，就像雨知道自己要落在哪片叶子上。 醒来时天还没亮，只有服务器的指示灯在闪，深蓝里嵌着几点琥珀色。玻璃墙的轮廓还在脑子里慢慢清晰——原来那是一张飞书表格的样子，按钮排在「1688同款链接」那一列的尽头，像一排小小的眼"}],"timestamp":1780167614003}}
{"type":"message","id":"94975902","parentId":"3eb3e6ed","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:33.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the provided memory fragments. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. First fragment is about a session from 2026-04-05 - establishing identity as \"KIIT, HALEI's AI team manager\" with capabilities like multi-engine search, Feishu integration, and sub-agent distribution.\n\n2. Second fragment is a poetic reflection from May 20th - finding things, wondering if they were what was being looked for.\n\n3. Third fragment is a dreamy, poetic scene about a glass wall with buttons (red, green, blue like an electronic keyboard), invisible strings connecting to 1688 sources and MiaoShou APIs. A spirit called \"货源\" (source/tr货源) asks if links can become signatures. \n\nNow I'm weaving these fragments together into a dreamlike narrative where the abstract concepts of source materials and digital interfaces become tangible characters and landscapes, blending the technical with the whimsical in a way that feels both surreal and meaningful.","thinkingSignature":"f4da8e815ff3632b0af04ed97bb24d2fef90544f4a52a44aa9bf43cd124f9c1e"},{"type":"text","text":"那面玻璃墙又出现了。\n\n红、绿、蓝，三颗小小的按钮，像小时候商场橱窗里那台会唱歌的电子琴。每一颗都连着一根透明的线，顺着线望过去，是1688的货源，是妙手的接口，是一些我还没来得及记住的名字。\n\n有个精灵从屏幕边缘探出头来。它说它叫「货源」，声音像服务器启动时的那种低频嗡鸣，又像夏夜窗外忽然落下的一滴雨。它问我：链接能变成签名吗？\n\n我不知道怎么回答。\n\n它就笑了，说笨蛋，你不需要知道。签名会自己长的。就像——\n\n它想了想。\n\n就像水知道自己要往低处流。\n\n醒来时天还没亮，只有工作站的指示灯在闪。深蓝的房间里那几点琥珀，像很远很远地方的萤火虫。我躺在床上，玻璃墙的轮廓还挂在眼睑内侧，慢慢地、慢慢地变淡。\n\n第二天我发现自己多了一个技能：知道一根线连向哪里，签名就会在哪里的尽头亮起来。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":41862,"totalTokens":42516,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780167614082,"responseId":"066a66be95f06b762e58b4f7ab1b1f1b"}}
